*** Context ***
+ Clear Workspace
+ A Project is created in the workspace without Execution Environment
+ A template is created
 
*** Actions ***
- Window -> Preferences
- Lua -> Editor -> Templates
- Select the template to export -> Export...
- Select the exported template -> Remove
- Import... -> Select the previously exported template
 
*** Assertions ***
# Check the imported template is in the templates list
# Check all the fields of the template correspond to the previously created/exported template
